PrecisApproval for the CHAMBRE DE COMMERCE DE ST-UBALD in Quebec (a) to change its name to "Chambre de commerce de la Seigneurie des Grondines", and (b) to change the boundaries of its district to St. Ubald, St. Casimir, St. Thuribe and Notre-Dame de Montauban.
Attachments
precis:
Approval for the CHAMBRE DE COMMERCE DE ST-UBALD in Quebec (a) to change
its name to "Chambre de commerce de la Seigneurie des Grondines", and
(b) to change the boundaries of its district to St. Ubald, St. Casimir,
St. Thuribe and Notre-Dame de Montauban.
